{
  "info": {
    "name": "M3Motors API",
    "description": "API completa de M3Motors — Gestión de talleres mecánicos y mantenimiento predictivo.\n\n## Autenticación\n\n**Mobile (JWT):** Login con `/auth/login-mobile` o registro con `/auth/register`. El token JWT se guarda en la variable `{{mobile_token}}`.\n\n**Web (Clerk):** Login desde el frontend web. El token Clerk se guarda en la variable `{{clerk_token}}`.\n\n## Variables de entorno\n\nUsar `M3Motors - Localhost` o `M3Motors - Producción`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "m3motors"
  },
  "variable": [],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth Mobile",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login Mobile",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"mathias.machin@m3motors.me\",\n  \"password\": \"M3motors2026!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login-mobile",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login-mobile"]
            },
            "description": "Login unificado para mecánicos y clientes. Si el usuario no tiene passwordHash, se guarda el password en el primer login."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Register Client",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"nombre\": \"Cliente Test\",\n  \"telefono\": \"0991234567\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Registro de cliente desde mobile. Retorna JWT."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth Web (Clerk)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Current User",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clerk_token}}" }
